cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.NI, cs.SY 

The paper focuses on security and energy-efficient computation offloading in mobile edge computing, which involves aspects of computer security (cs.CR), distributed computing (cs.DC), software engineering (cs.SE), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), and systems and control (cs.SY). However, since security is a major concern in the paper, cs.CR is the most likely sub-category.
